Sentece: After one or three doses of 5 mg/kg, peak plasma and tissue levels of AMPH were 1.7 +/- 0.2 and 2.9 +/- 0.3 microM in plasma, 36 +/- 6 and 73 +/- 10 in substantia nigra and 25 +/- 4 and 50 +/- 8 in caudate/putamen, respectively.
